name: 100 Jump
description: Can you jumping with 100 clicking the spacebar without falling?, try this game. Press "A" for Left and "D" for Right to control the player, be careful when jumping because there a tree with mesh collider in it, If wrong jumping you will be respawn, don't worry there a checkpoint, if almost finish you won't start them over. For Slowing press "S" key & For Run Fast press "W" key or Use arrow keys.
